        "subject": "LU-2182 llapi: Use new layout for lfs setstripe",
        "message": "LU-2182 llapi: Use new layout for lfs setstripe\n\nThis patch moves the lfs_setstripe and llapi_file_open\nfunctions to the new layout api. We also expand layout\napi to include a verification function of the layout\ncreated by the user. llapi_layout_verify test to see\nif the target lustre file system supports what the\nuser wants.\n\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@gmail.com>\nChange-Id: Ibdb1a0cca1fa5be5e7717f78883742342564def3\n"
      },
